title: Hi, I am Oliver.

---
content:

* Born in Germany on Star Wars day in the year the last man landed on the moon
* Used to compose and play [music](https://soundcloud.com/oliver-bestwalter)
* Then worked at a [factory](https://www.micronas.com/)
* Then - although "not good at math" - dared to study [Computer Engineering](https://www.hs-emden-leer.de/)
* Now software developer at [Avira](http://avira.com)

## Python & I

* I Love [Python](https://www.python.org/) - came for the language, stayed for the community
* When I am not [programming with Python](/projects), I like to [talk about it](https://pyvideo.org/speaker/oliver-bestwalter.html)
* I also like helping others to learn Python and [testing with Python](https://www.python-academy.com/courses/specialtopics/python_course_testing.html)

